snippet.title: Sonic Moon BETA stuff {28/10/2022} [More of W.I.P Demo 4]
snippet.description:
Decided to show off some more of Sonic Moon on YouTube. Here are some things:
* W.I.P FM soundtrack. Special thanks to Lunar Renegade for composing it. Since it's still incomplete, I can't say it'll be ready for the release of Demo 4, but hopefully it will be ready for the final release.
* W.I.P Brazilian Portuguese translation. Special thanks to Creative Araya.
* Tweaked Mighty gameplay. His hammer drop now causes monitors to fall from the sky.
* Tweaked Luna gameplay. She can now double-jump!
* Some changed and extended level design.
* Additional work on Super Stages.

0:29: Contrast Coast Zone Act 1
2:56: Contrast Coast Zone Act 2
4:10: Contrast Coast Zone Act 3
5:15: Legacy Luminance Zone Act 1
7:13: Ruby Ruins Zone Act 1
8:19: Mental Mountains Zone Act 2
9:23: Ample Aqua Zone Act 1
10:28: Ample Aqua Zone Act 2

Follow updates on Game Jolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/sonicthehedgehogmoon/568526

Creative Araya: https://www.youtube.com/c/JoaoAraya
Luna Renegade: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCN61yaS8labiYPX_DGoQxrw

Be sure to let me know what you think. I really don't know when this demo will release. Hopefully by the end of the year though.
By the way, this my first time using OBS. It's pretty neat!

Mario Obsessed - MMXXII
Looking forward to Halloween? I love watching The Real Ghostbusters.
